```python
def fibfib(n: int) -> int:
    fib_sequence = [0, 0, 1]
    if n < 3:
        return fib_sequence[n]

    for i in range(3, n + 1):
        fib_sequence.append(fib_sequence[i - 1] + fib_sequence[i - 2] + fib_sequence[i - 3])

    return fib_sequence[n]
```

